    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative example of the E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving masterpiece utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, providing a linear power band and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is structurally sound, having received comprehensive subframe reinforcement, while the rod bearing service has been performed as preventative maintenance. Power is transmitted through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The exterior retains its factory-correct finish with exceptional depth, free from rock chips or swirling. Inside, the Nappa leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, and the cockpit is devoid of the typical pixel failure in the instrument cluster. This is a mechanically sorted, collector-grade specimen with a fully documented service history.",
